description: Gets a list of parameters for a pipeline execution.

parameters.name: PipelineExecutionArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the pipeline execution.

nested_items.name: PipelineParameters
nested_items.description: Contains a list of pipeline parameters. This list can be empty.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the parameter to assign a value to. This parameter name must match a named parameter in the pipeline definition.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The literal value for the parameter.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the result of the previous ListPipelineParametersForExecution request was truncated, the response includes a NextToken. To retrieve the next set of parameters, use the token in the next request.
